methods.isResolvable:
Returns true if the resolver can resolve the uri.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the uri
:return: (boolean) true if this resolver can resolve uri
methods.resolve:
Resolve uri into an object.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the URI
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the object

Create a full snapshot of the remote URI. Uses SNAP_OPTIONS.

*Overload 1*

  :return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the table to snapshot
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param targetUri: (java.lang.String) - the target URI
  :param table: (io.deephaven.qst.table.TableSpec) - the table spec
  :return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the table to snapshot
  
*Overload 3*  
  :param target: (io.deephaven.uri.DeephavenTarget) - the target
